<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Select which field should be transferred to La Redoute as the item preview text. The item preview text has to be in French. Otherwise the item will not be exported.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Item description</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Select which field should be transferred to La Redoute as the item description. The item description has to be in French. Otherwise the item will not be exported.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Technical data</strong></p></td>
