<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Minimum additional delay in delivery</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Enter the duration in days. This number is added to your items' normal minimum delivery time.</p></td>
</tr>
