<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Create a customer for La Redoute and enter the customer’s ID here (see chapter 11).</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Book incoming payment</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Select whether orders from La Redoute should be marked as <strong>paid</strong> or <strong>open</strong> when they are imported. This decision has to be made since customers pay La Redoute and La Redoute pays you afterwards.</p></td>
