<p>Set up an <a href="/en/en/basics/automation/event-procedures">event procedure</a> to automatically send shipping confirmations to La Redoute. The shipping confirmation is automatically sent to La Redoute as soon as the order status changes to <strong>[7] Outgoing items booked</strong>. La Redoute automatically informs the buyer of the shipment.</p>
