<h2 id="1600">18. Viewing the API log</h2>
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>The menu <strong>Data » API log » Tab: API log</strong> contains a history of processes that run via the La Redoute interface. The <strong>LaRedoute</strong> format is available for La Redoute.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph instruction">
<p>Viewing the API log:</p>
</div>
<div class="olist arabic">
<ol class="arabic">
<li>
<p>Go to <strong>Data » API log » Tab: API log</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Select the format <strong>LaRedoute</strong> from the drop-down list <strong>Process</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Select a date if you only want to see entries for a specific day.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Select the number of results per page.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Click on <strong>Search</strong> to display the results.</p>
</li>
</ol>
</div>
